parameters:
Memimi: Well... I must change into my formal attire to
welcome the great leader.

The convenience store clerk is just a disguise! The true
identity of Shark Mountain Memimi is a top executive of the
secret organization "Ocean Predator Empire," one of the Four
Heavenly Kings, the monster noble Shark Duke!!

Underling: Ah, Lord Shark Duke...! Today, we're also
vigorously refining that powder! It sells as fast as we can
make it, what a lucrative business... hahaha!

Memimi: Heh heh, irresistible... It's time for a quality
inspection, hand me a pinch.

Underling: You sure do love it... But you should go easy on
the merchandise. Once you get a taste of this stuff, it's
not so easy to quit...!

Memimi: Hehehe... Mix this Powder A with water... then mix
in Powder B, and stir well until... the color changes...
heheheh...!

Underling: Hey, give me a taste too...! No one can resist
the allure of this "delicious powder," the organization's
biggest source of income...!

Memimi: It's often mistaken for something chemical, but it's
a powder made from healthy ingredients like purple cabbage
and gardenia fruits! It's even more exquisite when eaten
with crushed candy...
Shark Duke... It seems the business is going smoothly...

Memimi: Huh...! That voice! The great leader! Lord Shark
Broccoli---!!!

Shark Broccoli: The convenience store management... the sale
of delicious powder, and above all, the consecutive
victories in "Monster Fight." With yesterday's victory, our
organization has finally joined the ranks of the four major
organizations in the city.

Memimi: It is all thanks to your excellent leadership, great
leader! Soon, our organization will surely achieve the long-
cherished goal of unifying all organizations within Dorobou
City!!

Lord Shark Broccoli is the head of the organization that
Memimi and her colleagues belong to, and is also a well-
known monster in the city.

Although their numbers are small compared to other major
organizations, the Ocean Predator Empire has caused a stir
in the neighborhood as an extremely solid organization with
abundant funds from convenience store management and
delicious powder sales, combined with Shark Duke, one of the
city's top combatants...

Shark Broccoli: Likely from now on, we will be engaging in
battles over territory with the other three organizations.
The monsters we'll fight will be on a different level of
strength than before.

Memimi: The blood of monsters stirs within me! I am always
ready to fight. It's time to repay the debt I owe for when
you picked me up from the orphanage when I was on the brink
of collapse, great leader...!

The Monster Fight, which began to be held several years ago,
is the hope for those living in the city's underworld. The
battles between secret organizations that were once consumed
by strife and on the brink of mutual destruction have been
transformed into one-on-one fights according to rules,
reducing the number of casualties to zero.

The lawless warring states period of Dorobou City's
underworld is now rapidly consolidating organizations...
With the unification of the city by the strongest
organization, true peace may come at last... Everyone has
begun to harbor such dreams...

Shark Broccoli: That's why we can't let other
incomprehensible evil organizations dictate this
underworld... If heartless people gain power, an era of
lawlessness worse than before will come!

Memimi: I understand! For the peace of the city, I will
surely defeat all other organization's monsters and achieve
unification!!

As the representative monster of her organization, fighting
for territory, Memimi will face countless trials from now
on...

Memimi: Now then... today at the Monster Fight venue, I was
supposed to meet my next opponent. There's still time, so
before that, I'll do that thing in my room... and maybe take
a little stroll around town...
"Let's wander around the town or go to my\nroom!"
"The Tale of the Shark Monster, Duke Shark's\nEntrance!"
